Package: rtdown.molit
Type: Package
Title: Interactive MOLIT Apartment Real-Estate Transaction Downloader
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Derick S.", "Park", email = "soonmai@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Interactive command-line downloader for the Korean Ministry of
    Land, Infrastructure and Transport (MOLIT) apartment sale and rental
    transaction APIs ('RTMSDataSvcAptTrade' and 'RTMSDataSvcAptRent').
    The single entry point 'rtdown_apt()' walks the user through a
    sequence of menu prompts (자료 유형 → 시도 → 시군구 또는 시도 전체 →
    시작 연월 → 종료 연월) and returns a tidy 'tibble' of every
    transaction in the requested range. Designed to be the simplest possible
    front-end to the MOLIT public-data-portal APIs.
